# baseURI: https://spec.edmcouncil.org/fibo/ontology/master/latest/BE/LegalEntities/NorthAmericanEntities/USExampleExecutives/
# imports: https://spec.edmcouncil.org/fibo/ontology/master/latest/BE/LegalEntities/NorthAmericanEntities/USExampleEntities/
# imports: https://spec.edmcouncil.org/fibo/ontology/master/latest/BE/OwnershipAndControl/ControlParties/
